                "children": [
                    {
                        "data": {
                            "id": "m00003",
                            "created": 1784118466208,
                            "text": "不要按文件浏览；按「能力」看同一功能有几套实现",
                            "expandState": "collapse"
                        },
                        "children": []
                    },
                    {
                        "data": {
                            "id": "m00004",
                            "created": 1784118466209,
                            "text": "每条能力下：.x / seed / glue / C 应最终收敛到单一权威",
                            "expandState": "collapse"
                        },
                        "children": []
                    },
                    {
                        "data": {
                            "id": "m00005",
                            "created": 1784118466210,
                            "text": "发现 ≥2 套语义路径 → 记入问题分析文档，禁止再打补丁扩写",
                            "expandState": "collapse"
                        },
                        "children": []
